\begin_inset Formula $2$
\end_inset

.
 The only eigenspace of 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{H}_{2}$
\end_inset

 is spanned by 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -1+\rmi\end{array}\right)^{T}$
\end_inset

.
