 of mutually exclusive outcomes 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\family roman
\size normal
It is worth asking whether the state vectors in DQT can contain probabilistic
 information about measurement outcomes.
